---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro"
import Container from "@components/Container.astro"
---

<Layout title="About" description="About Robert Ritz">
  <Container>
    <article class="animate">
      <h1>About</h1>

      <p>
        I'm a builder and a writer. I've spent the last thirteen years in
        Mongolia, where I co-founded a furniture company, Precision Kraft, and a
        university — the <a
          href="https://aum.edu.mn"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">American University of Mongolia</a
        >, which I now serve as president — and am raising a family.
      </p>

      <p>
        I write about whatever question I can't let go of, and usually I can't
        let it go until the data answers it. For eight years those questions
        were about Mongolia. Now they're mostly about America, at <a
          href="https://americanmetrics.org"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">American Metrics</a
        >.
      </p>

      <p>
        I also send a weekly <a
          href="https://mongolia.robertritz.com"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Mongolia newsletter</a
        > of news, politics, and economics, and run <a
          href="https://data.mn"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">Data.mn</a
        >, a project to make Mongolia's statistics accessible and searchable.
      </p>

      <p>
        You can find me on <a
          href="https://x.com/RobertERitz"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer">X</a
        >, subscribe to my <a href="/rss.xml">RSS feed</a>, or reach me by <a
          href="mailto:robert@aum.edu.mn">email</a
        >.
      </p>
    </article>
  </Container>
</Layout>
